269
00:19:41,690 --> 00:19:45,700
Excuse me, are you Takagi-san?

270
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:47,700
Yes.

271
00:19:47,700 --> 00:19:49,700
I'm Izumi, the one who took your call.

272
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:52,700
