-We have no choice.

304
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:46,680
Mook has to stay home.

305
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:50,680
Okay, then. In preparation for the real deal tomorrow, let's do our final practice.

306
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:53,690
Get set.

